息不规律，导致生物钟紊乱。比如有时候早睡，有时候又很晚才睡，身体无法适应规律的睡眠节奏。 四、环境因素 1. 周围环境嘈杂、光线过亮或温度不适宜，会影响睡眠质量，让人难以入睡。例如，住在靠近马路的地方，晚上车辆噪音较大；或者房间的灯光太亮，没有营造出适合睡眠的氛围。 2. 睡前进行剧烈运动，会使身体处于兴奋状态，也不利于入睡。"},"attached_info":"CkAI6cGuueicqMglEAMaCTExMDkyNTMxMyCy+/q3BjAAOI0BQA5yCTczMjI0NTEzN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"23 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6d128afe30f235015e54539ac45a116f_xl.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1728048431.738566","card_id":"Q_559579842","target":{"id":559579842,"title":"《封神演义》女娲让妲己祸害商朝，成功后为什么又杀了妲己？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/559579842","type":"question","created":1665801317,"answer_count":53,"follower_count":109,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[284,34991,41634,52420,221519],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4I6cGuueicqMglEAMaCDg2NjMzNzMwIOW4qJoGMAA4bUAPcgk1NTk1Nzk4NDJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"5.8 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-76e8b5267d9ad3d5bca2d79345b20697_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1728048431.739479","card_id":"Q_668137539","target":{"id":668137539,"title":"如何给不懂棒球的人说明大谷翔平的厉害?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/668137539","type":"question","created":1727237838,"answer_count":96,"follower_count":109,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[32478,213857],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"只看过几部运动漫，不了解棒球规则的人"},"attached_info":"Cj8I6cGuueicqMglEAMaCTExMDc1MjM4MSDOnc63BjAAOG1AEHIJNjY4MTM3NTM5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"5.7 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx